OL,6,FA doctor who facilitated abortions for
OL,7,Ftwo women with much-wanted pregnancies
OL,8,Fwas not allowed to prescribe a #28
OL,9,Fanti-sickness drug due to cost-
OL,10,Feffectiveness rules in Wales.
