OL,3,CWomen driven to end pregnancies amid
OL,4,Crow over #28 drug
OL,6,FGeorgina Forbes, a specialist doctor
OL,7,Fin Gwent, revealed she facilitated
OL,8,Fterminations for two women who were
OL,9,Fsuffering from hyperemesis gravidarum
OL,10,F(HG) in a single week. HG, which
OL,11,Faffects about 3% of pregnancies, leads
OL,12,Fto extreme, persistent nausea and
OL,13,Fvomiting.
OL,15,F"Both pregnancies were very much
OL,16,Fplanned and wanted," she wrote during
OL,17,Fa Senedd Committee session. "Both had
OL,18,Fmultiple admissions and were on other
OL,19,Fmedical treatments which were not
OL,20,Fgiving adequate relief.
