OL,6,F"For the sake of their physical and
OL,7,Fmental health, they felt their only
OL,8,Foption was to terminate their much-
OL,9,Fwanted pregnancies ` inevitably having
OL,10,Fa further impact on their well-being."
OL,12,FShe warned of distress for the
OL,13,Fpatients and staff involved because
OL,14,FXonvea "may well be the medication
OL,15,Fthat provides symptomatic relief but
OL,16,Fdepartments are not allowed to
OL,17,Fprescribe it".
