OL,7,FSexual and Reproductive Healthcare's
OL,8,FWales committee, said Xonvea costs #28
OL,9,Ffor a 10-day supply ` "far less than
OL,10,Fthe cost of admission". She urged
OL,11,FWelsh ministers to ensure women are
OL,12,Fnot "left behind compared to other UK
OL,13,Fnations".
