OL,6,FIn 2019, the drug was rejected for
OL,7,Froutine use by the All-Wales Medicines
OL,8,FStrategy Group (AWMSG) ` which advises
OL,9,Fministers ` due to "insufficient"
OL,10,Fevidence of cost-effectiveness.
OL,11,FScotland reached a similar conclusion
OL,12,Fwhile access in England is
OL,13,Finconsistent.
