OL,6,FBut campaigners argue the decision is
OL,7,Fa false economy. Data submitted to the
OL,8,FSenedd's petitions committee
OL,9,Fhighlighted a two-night hospital
OL,10,Fadmission to rehydrate a woman with
OL,11,Fsevere sickness costs the NHS #850,
OL,12,Fwith ambulance call-outs costing a
OL,13,Ffurther #238.
OL,15,FSarah Spooner, from Monmouthshire,
OL,16,Fargued the "myopic approach" ignores
OL,17,Fthe costs of untreated sickness such
OL,18,Fas perinatal mental health support.
