OL,4,Crow over #28 drug
OL,6,FRhian Pope-Flood suffered with
OL,7,Fhyperemesis gravidarum (also known as
OL,8,FHG) during both her pregnancies. While
OL,9,Fshe continued with the pregnancies,
OL,10,Fshe was bedbound and endured multiple
OL,11,Fhospital trips.
OL,13,F"I couldnt keep any food down, it got
OL,14,Fto the point where i was struggling to
OL,15,Feat anything, drink anything. I think
OL,16,FI lost a stone in the space of a week.
OL,17,FIt was awful, I felt guilt for my
OL,18,Funborn baby, whether she was getting
OL,19,Fenough nutrients from me cause I was
OL,20,Fbarely eating anything."
