OL,6,FShe said that she felt so unwell she
OL,7,Funderstands women who feel they have
OL,8,Fno choice but to end their pregnancies.
OL,10,F"You're doing an amazing thing
OL,11,Fbringing life into this world, and you
OL,12,Fjust feel absolutely awful, and I know
OL,13,Fthere are some women who - and I can
OL,14,Fsee why some women would be driven to
OL,15,Fthis, i know there are a lot of women
OL,16,F- who can't go through with their
OL,17,Fpregnancy as it is so bad.
