OL,6,FWriting to the petitions committee,
OL,7,FWales' health secretary Jeremy Miles
OL,8,Fsaid the 2019 AWMSG appraisal remains
OL,9,Fthe "most up-to-date and comprehensive
OL,10,Fevaluation".
OL,12,FHe told the committee health boards
OL,13,Fcan make Xonvea available in certain
OL,14,Fcircumstances, with more than 1,140
OL,15,Fprescriptions issued between January
OL,16,Fand July 2025. He added that the
OL,17,Fmanufacturer was "unable" to provide
OL,18,Fupdated information to support a
OL,19,Freappraisal.
