OL,6,FA Welsh Government Spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Representatives of the All Wales
OL,8,FMedicines Strategy Group continue to
OL,9,Fengage with the manufacturer of Xonvea
OL,10,Fin the hope it will be able to provide
OL,11,Fan updated submission including cost-
OL,12,Feffectiveness data.
OL,14,F"Healthcare professionals across Wales
OL,15,Fmay prescribe a range of effective
OL,16,Ftreatments for women suffering extreme
OL,17,Fpregnancy sickness. These include
OL,18,FXonvea in exceptional cases where
OL,19,Fother treatments have failed. GPs in
OL,20,Fevery health board area in Wales
OL,21,Fregularly prescribe Xonvea."
